    end

    %% ============ EXPORTERS ============
    subgraph "Metric Exporters"
        NodeExporter["🖥️ Node Exporter<br/>Host Metrics: CPU, RAM, Disk"]
        RedisExporter["🔴 Redis Exporter<br/>Redis internal metrics"]
        PostgresExporter["🗄️ Postgres Exporter<br/>DB Performance Metrics"]
        BlackboxProbe["🌐 Blackbox Exporter<br/>Probing HTTP/SSL health"]
    end

    %% ============ INTERACTIONS ============

    %% Ingress routing
    Caddy -->|HTTP Traffic| Web
    Caddy -->|HTTP Traffic| PayloadAdmin
    Caddy -->|HTTP Traffic| PayloadAPI

    %% Web ↔ Backend interaction
    Web -->|Internal API<br/>Server Actions| ProxyLayer
    ProxyLayer -->|REST Calls| PayloadAPI
    ProxyLayer -->|Session Check| AuthModule

    %% PayloadAPI ↔ Data layer (via PgBouncer)
    PayloadAPI -->|SQL Queries| PgBouncer
    PgBouncer -->|Connection Pool to| Postgres
    PayloadAPI <-->|Distributed Cache| Redis
    PayloadAPI -->|Trigger Reindex| Queue

    %% Auth flows
    AuthModule -->|Session Store| Redis
    AuthModule -->|User/Verify queries| PgBouncer
    AuthModule -->|Send Email Verify| Email

    %% Worker ↔ Data
    Queue <-->|Pull Tasks from| Worker
    Worker -->|SQL Updates| PgBouncer
    Worker -->|Invalidate Cache| Redis
    Worker -->|Sync Index to| Meilisearch
    Worker -->|SMTP Send| Email
    Worker -->|Firebase Send| Push

    %% Search engine queries
    Meilisearch <-->|Client Query| Web
    Meilisearch <-->|Internal Query| PayloadAPI

    %% Direct Caching
    Web -.->|Check Cache| Redis
    PayloadAPI -.->|Check Cache| Redis

    %% Media Assets
    Web -->|Fetch Assets| CDN
    PayloadAPI -->|Upload Assets| CDN

    %% Observability flows
    Web -->|Push JSON Logs| Logger
    PayloadAPI -->|Push JSON Logs| Logger
    AuthModule -->|Push JSON Logs| Logger
    Worker -->|Push JSON Logs| Logger

    %% Prometheus scraping
    NodeExporter -->|/metrics| Prometheus
    RedisExporter -->|Query Info| Redis
    RedisExporter -->|/metrics| Prometheus
    PostgresExporter -->|SQL Queries| Postgres
    PostgresExporter -->|/metrics| Prometheus
    BlackboxProbe -->|HTTP Probes| Caddy
    BlackboxProbe -->|/metrics| Prometheus
    Web -->|App Metrics| Prometheus
    PayloadAPI -->|App Metrics| Prometheus
    Worker -->|App Metrics| Prometheus

    %% Visualization
    Grafana -->|Query Prometheus| Prometheus

    %% Alerting
    Prometheus -->|Fire Alert Rules| Alertmanager
    Alertmanager -->|Webhook Payload| AlertSink
    AlertSink -->|Notify Team| Push

    %% Data Backup
    Postgres -.->|Nightly Snapshot| Backup

